    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281420/extras/9d9b37be1384de8495408ed26bbe0576.poster.avif?t=1743681265\" width=736 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281420/extras/9d9b37be1384de8495408ed26bbe0576.webm?t=1743681265\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281420/extras/9d9b37be1384de8495408ed26bbe0576.mp4?t=1743681265\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong>无限的可能性</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281420/extras/d0191eaa59cbcce0a68feb7fecacdd75.poster.avif?t=1743681265\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281420/extras/d0191eaa59cbcce0a68feb7fecacdd75.webm?t=1743681265\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281420/extras/d0191eaa59cbcce0a68feb7fecacdd75.mp4?t=1743681265\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >PARADISE® 是一款拥有无限可能性的生活模拟游戏。<br>与朋友一起玩，参与枪战，赛车，完成日常任务，达到人生巅峰。赚取金钱，购买你想要的东西，从房地产到豪华衣物。<br>无尽的世界，无尽的游戏。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>人工智能驱动的NPC</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281420/extras/030fa8ba2482fec6975bd53533071503.poster.avif?t=1743681265\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281420/extras/030fa8ba2482fec6975bd53533071503.webm?t=1743681265\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3281420/extras/030fa8ba2482fec6975bd53533071503.mp4?t=1743681265\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >开放世界中的每个NPC不仅仅是背景角色。你可以通过聊天或语音与他们沟通。它们拥有真实的声音、情感和对你行动的反应，让它们像真正的活人一样行动。每个NPC都有自己的背景故事、工作和日常生活。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>现实世界模拟</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在PARADISE中，我们重建了一个完整的岛屿国家，拥有现实世界的所有特征，从拥有摩天大楼和繁忙城市区的城市风景，到宁静的海洋、沙滩和郁郁葱葱的热带森林。游戏中有不同的区块和自然区域，每个都经过精心设计，以增强真实感。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们的世界充满了不同种族和体型的人，繁忙的汽车遵守交通规则，商店、夜总会和工业物业充满活力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家可以通过游戏内的货币PAR参与现实经济，面对犯罪的后果，并追求各种关系，模拟现实生活的复杂性。</p>",
